OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of 'beautiful and kind' mother-
OL,5,Cof-two
OL,7,FA man has appeared in court after
OL,8,Fbeing charged with the murder a mother-
OL,9,Fof-two in Llanelli.
OL,11,FThe body of Sophie Evans, 30, was
OL,12,Ffound in a house on Bigyn Road, in
OL,13,FLlanelli, Carmarthenshire, on 5 July.
OL,15,FA murder enquiry was launched, with
OL,16,FRichard Jones, of Y Rhodfa in Burry
OL,17,FPort, arrested later that day.
OL,19,FOfficers have since charged the 49-
OL,20,Fyear-old, who was known to Sophie,
OL,21,Fwith her murder.
