OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of 'beautiful and kind' mother-
OL,5,Cof-two
OL,7,FJones appeared at Llanelli Magistrates
OL,8,FCourt this morning (Friday 12 July).
OL,10,FPaying tribute to her, Sophie's family
OL,11,Fsaid: "Our beautiful and amazing
OL,12,Fsister and daughter Sophie was
OL,13,Ftragically taken from us, and our
OL,14,Flives will never be the same.
OL,16,F"We are heartbroken by our loss. Our
OL,17,FSophie, only 30 years young, will be
OL,18,Fgreatly missed by us all.
