OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of 'beautiful and kind' mother-
OL,5,Cof-two
OL,7,F"She was a loving mother to her two
OL,8,Fgirls, who she adored with all her
OL,9,Fheart. An amazing sister, who was the
OL,10,Frock of our family. So bright and
OL,11,Ffunny, always making us laugh.
OL,13,F"Sophie was a loving daughter, with a
OL,14,Fhuge heart, who we all adored. She
OL,15,Flived life to the fullest, and will be
OL,16,Fremembered for being so kind and
OL,17,Fcaring to her loved ones.
