OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of 'beautiful and kind' mother-
OL,5,Cof-two
OL,7,F"Sophie loved spending time with her
OL,8,Fchildren and family, had a passion for
OL,9,Fbeauty therapy, and enjoyed keeping up
OL,10,Fwith her fitness and the latest
OL,11,Ffashion trends.
OL,13,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,14,Ftheir support at this horrific time.
OL,15,FIt has meant a lot to the whole
OL,16,Ffamily. We would now like time to
OL,17,Fgrieve, and ask to be given privacy in
OL,18,Fwhich to do so."
