OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of 'beautiful and kind' mother-
OL,5,Cof-two
OL,7,FA Dyfed-Powys Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with Sophie's
OL,9,Ffamily at this time, and they continue
OL,10,Fto receive support from specialist
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,F"The investigation team is grateful
OL,14,Ffor the support of the community while
OL,15,Fenquiries have been carried out."
OL,17,FJones was been remanded into custody
OL,18,Fand will appear before Swansea Crown
OL,19,FCourt on Monday (July 15).
